	]br
	$LF
	"Values of speed are in units of 0.25 km/h.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Values of acceleration are in units of 0.25 km/h per frame.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Rotation is in units of 1/65536 of full revolution.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"All values represented in decimal, base 10.
	$LF
